      "text": "Components:\n1. Study material inputs:\n Text books, Notes, Pdfs, slides\n2. Content analysis module:\nUnderstands what student wants to leanr.\nTechnical: NLP, Key word extraction, Topic modeling\nconcept hierarchy creation.\nOutput: Key concepts, Sub topics, difficutly classification\n3. AI Orchestrator - Smart StudyBuddy.\n Responsible for : Coordinating modules, selecting explanations and questions\nAdjusting difficulty, Personalization decisions\n\n4. LLM Module Query generations\n   Multiple choice questions, Short answers, Case-based problems,\n   conceptual questions\n  Adaptive: Easy -> Medium->Hard, Different phrasings, Application baeed\nquesstions\n\n5. Progress tracking _ SQlite DB\n  It stores: Topics attenpted, Accuracy score, Time spent, \nLearning style preferance,  master level per concepts.\n\n6. Adaptive Learning\n   Reteach weak areas, Switch explation styile, increase difficulty on mastery.\nsimple ML scoring\n\n7. Study Schedule GEnerator\n  Uses spaced repition, adjusts based on availability & perfoirmance\n8. Student interface\n Dashboard, Quizzes, Explanations, Progress visualizations, Studt reminders\n\n\n",
